{"type": "article", "id": 8046, "title": "Soma “世上最美”净水器", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-02T07:44:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052346529zrZPg2lVcKHYbFX.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这款净水器被称为是“世界上最美丽的净水器”，它采用玻璃的材料，遵循极简主义设计风格，外形圆润可爱，过滤器由纯天然物质与生物降解物料组成，净水功能强大。按照容量，有 48 和 60 盎司型号可以选择，起价是 39 美元，<a href=\"https://www.drinksoma.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。购买还能够给<a href=\"http://www.charitywater.org/\" target=\"_blank\"> Charity: Water </a>捐钱。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234650yoXVhR9NrlCm2QWB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68027211\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234650ozdhEYxDQ4IsyOcm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.85910653\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234651olNhK0xTqDr6j7Yy.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66133333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234651U4NdJBPm5nyEDuqf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.78369906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}